Key.Original: Attention, the enemy launches a saboteur attack on the base...
Key.Spanish: Atención, el enemigo lanza un ataque de saboteador en la base....
Key.Portuguese: Atenção, o inimigo lança um ataque sabotador na base..
Key.Korean: 주의, 적 특수부대가 아군 기지에 사포타주를 실시합니다...
Key.Japanese: 注意！ 敵が基地に工作員を送り込んでいる。
Key.English: ВНИМАНИЕ: диверсанты противника на нашей БАЗЕ!
Key.Russian: ВНИМАНИЕ: диверсанты противника на нашей БАЗЕ!
Key.Chinesesimp: 注意，敌人在基地发动破坏攻击...
Key.Chinese: 注意，敵人在基地發動破壞攻擊...
Key.French: Attention, l'ennemi lance une attaque de saboteur sur la base...
Key.Czech: Pozor: sabotéři nepřítele na naší základně!
Key.German: ACHTUNG: Feindliche Saboteure auf unserer BASIS!
Key.Hungarian: Figyelem: ellenséges szabotőrök vannak a bázisunkon!
Key.Italian: Attenzione: sabotatori nemici sulla nostra base!
Key.Polish: Uwaga: dywersanci wroga w naszej bazie!

Key.Original: Hmm. Interresting. Codenames used when they are launching attack on our base. Could be useful.
Key.Spanish: Hmm Interesante. Los nombres en clave se usan cuando están lanzando ataques contra nuestra base. Podría ser útil.
Key.Portuguese: Hmm. Interresting. Nomes de códigos usados quando estão lançando ataque em nossa base. Podem ser úteis.
Key.Korean: 음. 흥미롭습니다. 적군이 우리기지를 공격할 때 사용되는 코드네임 입니다. 유용 할 수도 있습니다.
Key.Japanese: Hmm. Interresting. Codenames used when they are launching attack on our base. Could be useful.
Key.English: Hmm. Interresting. Codenames used when they are launching attack on our base. Could be useful.
Key.Russian: Получен код, используемый при начале атаки на нашу базу. Нам будет полезно!
Key.Chinesesimp: 嗯。很有趣。他们攻击我们基地时使用的代号。可能有用。
Key.Chinese: 嗯，有意思的。他們在我們基地發動攻擊時使用的代號。可能有用。
Key.French: Hmm. Intéressant. Les noms de code utilisés lorsqu'ils lancent une attaque sur notre base. Cela pourrait être utile.

Key.Japanese: 自軍基地の破壊:
情報送信中... 待機してください。
情報送信

Key.Original: The data terminal was destroyed before the data was uploaded!
Key.Spanish: El terminal de datos se destruyó antes de que se cargaran los datos.
Key.Portuguese: O terminal de dados foi destruído antes de os dados serem carregados
Key.Korean: 데이터를 업로드하기 전에 데이터 터미널이 파괴되었습니다
Key.Japanese: 情報を送信する前に端末が破壊された。
Key.English: The data terminal was destroyed before the data was uploaded
Key.Russian: Терминал был уничтожен до того, как разведданные успели выгрузить
Key.Chinesesimp: 数据终端在数据上传之前被销毁了！
Key.Chinese: 上傳數據之前，數據終端已損壞！
Key.French: Le terminal de données a été détruit avant le téléchargement des données!

Key.Original: We know the location of an enemy data terminal with important data. Get there and upload the data to one of our servers!
Key.Spanish: Conocemos la ubicación de una terminal de datos enemiga con datos importantes. Llegue allí y suba los datos a uno de nuestros servidores.!
Key.Portuguese: Nós sabemos a localização de um terminal de dados inimigo com dados importantes. Chegue lá e faça o upload dos dados para um de nossos servidores!
Key.Korean: 우리는 중요한 데이터를 포함하고 있는 적군의 데이터 터미널의 위치를 알고 있습니다. 데이터 터미널을 획득하고 우리의 서버들중 하나에 데이터를 업로드 하세요!
Key.Japanese: 重要情報の入った情報端末の場所が分かった。 端末を捜索し、我々のサーバーに情報を送信せよ！
Key.English: We know the location of an enemy data terminal with important data. Get there and upload the data to one of our servers!
Key.Russian: Мы обнаружили терминал противника с важными данными. Выдвигайтесь и скачайте все данные для нас!
Key.Chinesesimp: 我们知道具有重要数据的敌方数据终端的位置。到那里并将数据上传到我们的服务器之一！
Key.Chinese: 我們知道具有重要資料的敵資料伺服器的位置。到達那裡並將資料上傳到我們的伺服器之一！
Key.French: Nous connaissons l'emplacement d'un terminal de données ennemi contenant des données importantes. Allez-y et téléchargez les données sur l'un de nos serveurs!
Key.Czech: Našli jsme nepřátelský terminál s důležitými údaji. Vydejte se a stáhněte si všechna data pro nás!
Key.German: Wir haben ein gegnerisches Terminal mit wichtigen Daten gefunden. Kommen Sie voran und laden Sie alle Daten für uns herunter!
Key.Hungarian: Megtaláltuk az ellenség terminálját fontos adatokkal. Jöjjön és töltse le nekünk az összes adatot!
Key.Italian: Abbiamo trovato un terminale nemico con dati importanti. Vai avanti e scarica tutti i dati per noi!
Key.Polish: Znaleźliśmy Terminal wroga z ważnymi danymi. Śmiało i pobierz wszystkie dane dla nas!
Key.Turkish: Düşman terminalini önemli verilerle bulduk. Öne çıkın ve tüm verileri bizim için indirin!

Key.Original: Fantastic! You have uploaded the data!
Key.Portuguese: Fantástico! Você já fez o upload dos dados!
Key.Japanese: 素晴らしい! あなたはデータ送信を完了した!
Key.English: Fantastic! You have uploaded the data!
Key.French: Fantastique! Vous avez téléchargé les données!

Key.Japanese: データ送信完了!

Key.Original: The enemy is using a weird device to create earthquakes. Your mission, destroy it!
Key.Spanish: El enemigo está usando un dispositivo avanzado para crear terremotos. Tu misión, destrúyela!
Key.Portuguese: O inimigo está usando um dispositivo esquisito para criar terremotos. Sua missão, destrua-o!
Key.Korean: 적군이 기괴한 장비를 이용해 지진을 발생시키고 있습니다. 당신의 임무는, 그것을 파괴하는것입니다!
Key.Japanese: The enemy is using a weird device to create earthquakes. Your mission, destroy it!
Key.English: The enemy is using a weird device to create earthquakes. Your mission, destroy it!
Key.Russian: Противник использует устройство для создания искусственных землетрясений! Найдите и уничтожьте его!
Key.Chinesesimp: 敌人正在使用一种奇怪的装置来制造地震。你的使命，摧毁它！
Key.Chinese: 敵人正在使用一種奇怪的裝置來製造地震。你的使命，摧毀它！
Key.French: L'ennemi utilise un appareil étrange pour créer des tremblements de terre. Votre mission, détruisez-le!
Key.Czech: Nepřítel používá zařízení k vytvoření umělých zemětřesení! Najděte ho a zničte ho!
Key.German: Der Feind benutzt das Gerät, um künstliche Erdbeben zu erzeugen! Finde es und zerstöre es!
Key.Hungarian: Az ellenség a készüléket mesterséges földrengések létrehozására használja! Találd meg és pusztítsd el!
Key.Italian: Il nemico utilizza il dispositivo per creare terremoti artificiali! Trovatelo e distruggetelo!
Key.Polish: Wróg używa urządzenia do tworzenia sztucznych trzęsień ziemi! Znajdź i zniszcz go!
Key.Turkish: Düşman yapay depremler yaratmak için cihazı kullanıyor! Onu bulun ve yok edin!

Key.Original: Good job! The device was destroyed.
Key.Spanish: Buen trabajo! El dispositivo fue destruido.
Key.Portuguese: Bom trabalho! O aparelho foi destruído.
Key.Japanese: Good job! The device was destroyed.
Key.English: Good job! The device was destroyed.
Key.French: Bon travail! L'appareil a été détruit.

Key.Original: An enemy SAM site gives us a lot of trouble. Destroy the radar and the SAM launcher!
Key.Spanish: Un lanzador SAM enemigo nos causa muchos problemas. Destruye el radar y el lanzador SAM!
Key.Portuguese: Um site inimigo da SAM nos dá muitos problemas. Destrua o radar e o lançador do SAM!
Key.Korean: 적군의 지대공미사일 부대가 아군에게 많은 문제가 되고 있습니다. 레이더와 지대공미사일 런처를 파괴하세요!
Key.Japanese: An enemy SAM site gives us a lot of trouble. Destroy the radar and the SAM launcher!
Key.English: An enemy SAM site gives us a lot of trouble. Destroy the radar and the SAM launcher!
Key.Russian: ПВО противника доставляет нам много хлопот. Уничтожьте РЛС и пусковую установку!
Key.Chinesesimp: 敌人的SAM网站给我们带来了很多麻烦。摧毁雷达和SAM发射器！
Key.Chinese: 敵人的SAM網站給我們帶來了很多麻煩。摧毀雷達和SAM發射器！
Key.French: Un site SAM ennemi nous cause beaucoup de problèmes. Détruisez le radar et le lanceur SAM!
Key.Czech: Protivníkova obrana nám dělá hodně starostí. Zničte radar a spouštěč!
Key.German: Die feindliche Luftabwehr bereitet uns viel Ärger. Zerstöre das Radar und den Launcher!
Key.Hungarian: Az ellenség légvédelme sok bajt okoz nekünk. Pusztítsd el a radart és a rakétavetőt!
Key.Italian: La difesa aerea nemica ci dà un sacco di problemi. Distruggi il radar e il lanciatore!
Key.Polish: Obrona przeciwna wroga sprawia nam wiele kłopotów. Zniszcz radar i wyrzutnię!
Key.Turkish: Düşman hava savunması bize çok sıkıntı veriyor. Radarı ve fırlatıcıyı yok edin!

Key.Original: Good work! The SAM site is out of business.
Key.Spanish: ¡Buen trabajo! El sitio de SAM está fuera del negocio.
Key.Portuguese: Bom trabalho! O site da SAM está fora do ar.
Key.Japanese: Good work! The SAM site is out of business.
Key.English: Good work! The SAM site is out of business.
Key.Russian: Отличная работа! Система ПВО выведена из строя.
Key.Chinese: 幹得好！ SAM網站已關閉。
Key.French: Bon travail! Le site SAM est détruit.

Key.Original: You were not able to clear the mines fast enough...
Key.Spanish: No pudiste limpiar las minas lo suficientemente rápido...
Key.Portuguese: Você não foi capaz de limpar as minas rápido o suficiente...
Key.Korean: 귀관은 지뢰를 충분히 신속하게 제거하지 못했다...
Key.Japanese: You were not able to clear the mines fast enough...
Key.English: You were not able to clear the mines fast enough...
Key.Russian: Вы не смогли быстро разминировать минное поле...
Key.Chinesesimp: 你无法足够快地清除地雷...
Key.Chinese: 您無法足夠快地清除地雷...
Key.French: Vous n'avez pas pu nettoyer les mines assez rapidement...

Key.Original: Your task is to search for a weapon cache reported by locals and destroy it! You have about 30 minutes for solving the task
Key.Spanish: ¡Tu tarea es buscar un caché de armas reportado por los lugareños y destruirlo! Tienes unos 30 minutos para resolver la tarea.
Key.Portuguese: Sua tarefa é procurar por um cache de armas reportado pelos locais e destruí-lo! Você tem cerca de 30 minutos para resolver a tarefa
Key.Korean: 귀관의 임무는 지역주민들이 제보한 무기 은닉처를 찾아 파괴하는것입니다! 귀관은 이 임무를 30분내로 해결 해야합니다
Key.Japanese: Your task is to search for a weapon cache reported by locals and destroy it! You have about 30 minutes for solving the task
Key.English: Your task is to search for a weapon cache reported by locals and destroy it! You have about 30 minutes for solving the task
Key.Russian: Ваша задача найти схрон с оружием неонацистов и уничтожить его! У вас 30 минут на выполнение задачи.
Key.Chinesesimp: 你的任务是搜索当地人报告的武器库并销毁它！你有大约30分钟的时间来解决任务
Key.Chinese: 你的任務是搜索當地人報告的武器庫並銷毀它！你有大約30分鐘的時間來解決任務
Key.French: Votre tâche consiste à rechercher une cache d'armes signalé par les habitants et à la détruire! Vous disposez d'environ 30 minutes pour résoudre la tâche
Key.Czech: Vaším úkolem je najít schron se zbraní teroristů a zničit ho! Máte 30 minut na dokončení úkolu.
Key.German: Ihre Aufgabe ist es, das Lagerhaus mit den Waffen der Terroristen zu finden und es zu zerstören! Sie haben 30 Minuten Zeit, um die Aufgabe zu erledigen.
Key.Hungarian: Az Ön feladata, hogy megtalálja a cache terrorista fegyverek és elpusztítani! 30 perc áll rendelkezésére a feladat elvégzéséhez.
Key.Italian: Il vostro compito è quello di trovare un nascondiglio con le armi dei terroristi e distruggerlo! Hai 30 minuti per completare l'attività.
Key.Polish: Twoim zadaniem jest znaleźć skrzynkę z bronią terrorystów i zniszczyć ją! Masz 30 minut na wykonanie zadania.
Key.Turkish: Senin görevin teröristlerin silahlarıyla bir kasa bulmak ve onu yok etmek! Görevi tamamlamak için 30 dakikanız var.

Key.Original: Good job! The cache is destroyed
Key.Portuguese: Bom trabalho! O cache é destruído
Key.Japanese: Good job! The cache is destroyed
Key.English: Good job! The cache is destroyed
Key.French: Bon travail! La cache est détruit

Key.Original: The supply truck was destroyed before it could reach the point of destination.
Key.Spanish: El camión de suministros fue destruido antes de que pudiera llegar al punto de destino..
Key.Portuguese: O caminhão de abastecimento foi destruído antes que pudesse chegar ao ponto de destino.
Key.Korean: 보급트럭이 목표 지점에 도달하기 전에 파괴하십시오.

Key.French: Le camion de ravitaillement a été détruit avant d'atteindre le point de destination.

Key.Original: Attention!!!!\n\nAI is only allowed to drive a vehicle if a player is inside the vehicle!
Key.Spanish: ¡Atención !!!!\n\nAI solo puede conducir un vehículo si un jugador está dentro del vehículo!
Key.Portuguese: Attention!!!!\n\nAI só é permitido dirigir um veículo se um jogador estiver dentro do veículo!
Key.Korean: 주의!!!!\n\nAI 드라이버는 플레이어가 차량에 탑승하고 있을때만 허락됩니다!
Key.Japanese: Attention!!!!\n\nAI is only allowed to drive a vehicle if a player is inside the vehicle!
Key.English: Внимание!!!!\n\nБот может быть только водителем техники, если игрок внутри неё!
Key.Russian: Внимание!!!!\n\nБот может быть только водителем техники, если игрок внутри неё!
Key.Chinesesimp: 注意!!!!\n\n如果玩家在车内，AI只允许驾驶车辆！
Key.Chinese: 注意!!!!\n\n如果玩家在車內，AI只允許駕駛車輛！
Key.French: Attention!!!!\n\nL'IA n'est autorisé à conduire un véhicule que si un joueur est à l'intérieur du véhicule!
